&lt;p&gt;As an FDE, you’ll work closely with both Product and GTM teams, combining technical expertise with customer-facing skills to build innovative solutions that accelerate complex scientific workflows. We expect our FDEs to operate autonomously, thrive under ambiguity, and represent Manifold at the highest level in customer environments. Working at the intersection of AI and life sciences, you&#39;ll not only play a key role in Manifold&#39;s success but also help our customers bring life-changing medicines to patients faster.&lt;/p&gt;
