&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Embed directly with Manifold customers to understand their research environments and workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support Terra.bio and its user migration to the Manifold platform, serving as a technical bridge between existing Terra workflows and Manifold&#39;s new infrastructure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scope and architect end-to-end solutions leveraging Manifold&#39;s AI platform to solve customers’ most pressing problems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive rapid time-to-value by ensuring fast onboarding, successful pilots, and clear paths to platform adoption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and deliver technical artifacts purpose-built for customers: Data pipelines, agent configuration, process automation, and domain-specific tooling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot complex issues across infrastructure, data, and application layers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify repeatable patterns, playbooks, and tooling that accelerate future deployments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the core platform team to inform product roadmaps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current regarding AI industry advancements and life sciences infrastructure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
